title: Household and Community Statistics by Province, Italy, 2008
name: Household and Community Statistics by Province, Italy, 2008
description:
This datasets contains demographic data for Italy. In particular this data is on Households and communities by province in 2008. 

The source for the data is ISTAT - Istituto nazionale di statistica. They are basically the group that control Italian Census Statistics. Data are collected from the Population Register Offices and are updated from time to time with the last available year.
